Mutate {1}{U}{B}
Whenever you cast an instant or sorcery card from your graveyard, Xolithna, Orbital Banshee connives. [i](Draw a card, then discard a card. If you discarded a nonland card, put a +1/+1 counter on this creature.)[/i]
Spells you cast from your graveyard cost {1} less to cast.
